Modifications
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  This fork introduces modifications and additions on top of the original
  GLPI codebase. The original source code is preserved unmodified under the
  `.legacy/` directory for reference. All new and modified code is located
  outside of `.legacy/`.

  Modified by: Heitor Rapcinski
  Fork started: 2026

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Upstream Baseline
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  The `.legacy/` directory contains the upstream GLPI source code as it
  existed at the time this fork was created (based on the 11.0.x branch).
  It is kept read-only as a reference baseline and must not be modified.

